  "title": "이수한의원이 &#39;고운맘카드&#39; 지정 요양병원으로 등록되었습니다.",
  "addDate": "2013. 5. 13.",
  "categoryNo": "24",
  "parentCategoryNo": "8",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110168004804",
  "html_size": 180647,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110168004804\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110168004804\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p>2013년 4월 1일부터 이수한의원에서 고운맘카드를 이용하실 수 있습니다. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7e52c149722bba34.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"767\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1032px\" id=\"20130513_180/isuhani_13684150073070VvSG_JPEG/201304151233300641.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A68658C4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7e52c149722bba34.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>임신 중</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>입덧</p>\r\n<p>유산기, 태기불안</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>산후 치료, 부종치료, 어혈치료&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>산후풍의 예방과 치료</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>유산후 치료</p>\r\n<p>등</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>임신과 출산, 출산 후 과정에서 필요한</p>\r\n<p>진료와 치료, 처방을</p>\r\n<p>이수한의원에서 고운맘카드를 활용해서 받으실 수 있게 되었습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>감사합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130513_85/isuhani_1368415047755TUYcF_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 193px; rheight: 48px\" id=\"20130513_85/isuhani_1368415047755TUYcF_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A68658C4')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130513_85/isuhani_1368415047755TUYcF_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
